quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  24,32,aur apni qoum ki bewa aurton ke nikah kardiya karo. aur apne ghulamoo aur londion ke bhi jo naik hon ( nikah kardiya karo ) agar woh muflis hon ge to khuda un ko apne fazl se khush haal kardey ga. aur khuda ( bohat ) wusat wala aur ( sab kuch ) jan-nay wala hai
  24,33,aur jin ko bayah ka Maqdoor nah ho woh pak damni ko ikhtiyar kiye rahen yahan taq ke khuda un ko apne fazl se ghanni kardey. aur jo ghulam tum se makatbat chahain agar tum un mein ( salahiyat aur ) neki pao to un se mukatbat karlo. aur khuda ne jo maal tum ko bakhsha hai is mein se un ko bhi do. aur apni londion ko agar woh pak daman rehna chahain to ( be sharmi se ) dunyawi zindagi ke fawaid haasil karne ke liye badkaari par majaboor nah karna. aur jo un ko majaboor kere ga to un ( bechariyon ) ke majaboor kiye jaane ke baad khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  24,34,aur hum ne tumhari taraf roshan ayatain nazil ki hain aur jo log tum se pehlay guzar chuke hain un ki khabrain aur parhaiz garon ke liye nasiyaat
  24,35,khuda asmano aur zameen ka noor hai. is ke noor ki misaal aisi hai ke goya aik taaq hai jis mein chairag hai. aur chairag aik Qandil mein hai. aur Qandil ( aisi saaf shafaaf hai ke ) goya moti ka sa chamakta howa rarah hai is mein aik mubarak darakht ka tail jalaya jata hai ( yani ) Zaitoon ke nah mashriq ki taraf hai nah maghrib ki taraf. ( aisa maloom hota hai ke ) is ka tail khuwa aag usay nah bhi chovay julne ko tayyar hai ( pari ) roshni par roshni ( ho rahi hai ) khuda apne noor se jis ko chahta hai seedhi raah dekhata hai. aur khuda ne ( jo misalein ) bayan farmata hai ( to ) logon ke ( samjhane ke ) liye aur khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  24,36,( woh Qandil ) un gharon mein ( hai ) jin ke baray mein khuda ne irshad farmaya hai ke buland kiye jayen aur wahan khuda ke naam ka zikarkiya jaye ( aur ) un mein subah vsham is ki tasbeeh karte rahen
